cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.OH, cs.SE, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on creating a communication network for autonomous vehicles using small satellites. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the integration of a satellite software defined radio on an unmanned air vehicle. 
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper touches on various aspects of computer science, including small satellites, autonomous vehicles, and oceanography. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the development of a test platform and system of systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the creation of a cooperative network of autonomous vehicles and small satellites.
